S10E1.title: The One After Joey and Rachel Kiss
S10E1.des:
Ross has kissed Charlie although she is still
                officially dating Joey. Joey and Rachel have kissed as well, but they agonize over how to tell Ross.

S10E2.title: The One Where Ross Is Fine
S10E2.des:
Rachel, Joey and Charlie attend an uncomfortable
                dinner party at Ross's apartment. Former surrogate mother Phoebe is visited by her brother, Frank
                Jr.

S10E3.title: The One with Ross's Tan
S10E3.des:
Monica and Phoebe's annoying friend visits,
                causing a rift between the women. Ross goes to a tanning salon but fails to follow the directions.

S10E4.title: The One with the Cake
S10E4.des:
When Ross dashes out to help Rachel for Emma's
                birthday party, he leaves Joey in charge of keeping everybody in the apartment until they return.

S10E5.title: The One Where Rachel's Sister Babysits
S10E5.des:
Rachel thinks her annoying, self-indulgent
                younger sister, Amy, is finally on the verge of making a major change in her attitude.

S10E6.title: The One with Ross's Grant
S10E6.des:
Ross has the chance to receive a grant, but must
                break up with Charlie to get it. Phoebe tries to give a hideous painting to Monica and Rachel.

S10E7.title: The One with The Home Study
S10E7.des:
Phoebe and Mike opt to have a small wedding and
                donate the extra money to a children's charity -- only to demand it all back later.

S10E8.title: The One with the Late Thanksgiving
S10E8.des:
Monica prepares a fabulous Thanksgiving feast
                for the gang, but she becomes furious when everyone arrives late to the gathering.

S10E9.title: The One with the Birth Mother
S10E9.des:
Nervous and excited, Monica and Chandler travel
                to Ohio to meet a pregnant woman who is considering allowing them to adopt her child when it's born.

S10E10.title: The One Where Chandler Gets Caught
S10E10.des:
When Phoebe and Rachel see Chandler getting into
                a car with a pretty woman during work hours, they follow him.

S10E11.title: The One Where the Stripper Cries
S10E11.des:
Joey appears as a celebrity contestant on "The
                $100,000 Pyramid," but his dubious IQ puts his partner's prize money at risk.

S10E12.title: The One with Phoebe's Wedding
S10E12.des:
Phoebe's wedding planner, Monica, is driving
                everyone around her crazy. Chandler and Ross lobby Rachel to choose one of them as a groomsman.

S10E13.title: The One Where Joey Speaks French
S10E13.des:
Monica and Chandler show Erica, the mother of
                the unborn baby they want to adopt, the sights of New York. Joey implores Phoebe to teach him
                French.

S10E14.title: The One with Princess Consuela
S10E14.des:
Rachel nearly gags on her meal when she goes on
                a job interview at a restaurant and sits next to her current boss. Phoebe considers changing her
                name.

S10E15.title: The One Where Estelle Dies
S10E15.des:
When Rachel makes a startling announcement, Ross
                schemes to get her former job back for her. Joey is flustered by the upheaval in his friends' lives.

S10E16.title: The One with Rachel's Going Away Party
S10E16.des:
As Rachel prepares to leave for Paris, the gang
                hosts a farewell party for her. But one friend is offended when he is excluded.

S10E17.title: The Last One: Part 1 & Part 2
S10E17.des:
On their last day together, Rachel, Monica,
                Phoebe, Joey, Chandler and Ross reflect on their shared times with bittersweet emotion.

year:
The touching final season of this Emmy-winning sitcom
            wraps up the stories of the Manhattan sextet, including Ross and Rachel's on-and-off romance.
